item.content:encoded:
Make has a blog entry about a VW jet car. This is just strange. One, why in the world would you put this in a VW Beetle? A Beetle isn’t known as the most impressive vehicle in the land, plus it doesn’t exactly lend itself design wise to mounting a rocket. Wouldn’t a truck be better for this?

Despite the odd choice of cars, this looks awesome. Only one question left, how fast does it go?
